Welcome to my first NFT: 

This NFT piece is a fusion of 3d modeling, pixel art and drawing.The position of the objects have a minimalist essence.

The arm of a girl rendered, with the meaning of an UV tattoo of a wild female spirit connected with nature, manifesting magick through symbols. This girl loves her bracelet, she can't stop seeing its interactive colors every time she turns it on. Produces energy and connects it with the creation of reality.
